<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-29T16:37:34-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-29T16:37:34-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-29T16:37:34-04:00</updated><title>加州州长否决重大人工智能安全法案</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;红色电路板上大脑的照片插图。&quot; src =“ https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/yhyxdmmdlbe1dfybcsgijrakdyq=/0x0:2040x1360/131 “ />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |图片来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;MGZI28&quot;>;加州州长 Gavin Newsom 否决了《前沿人工智能模型安全创新法案》&lt;a href=&quot;https://leginfo.legislature.ca .gov/faces/billTextClient.xhtml?bill_id=202320240SB1047&quot;>;(SB 1047&lt;/a>;) 今天。纽瑟姆州长在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/25178071-sb-1047-veto-message?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;否决消息&lt;/a>;中列举了多种因素在他的决定中，包括该法案会给人工智能公司带来的负担、加州在该领域的领先地位，以及对该法案可能过于宽泛的批评。&lt;/p>; &lt;blockquote>;&lt;p id=&quot;tsMFKU&quot;>;“虽然SB 1047 出于善意，并未考虑人工智能系统是否部署在高风险环境中、涉及关键决策或敏感数据的使用。相反，该法案甚至对最基本的功能都采用了严格的标准——只要大型系统部署它。我不认为这是保护公众免受真正威胁的最佳方法...&lt;/p>;&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29 /24232172/california-ai-safety-bill-1047-vetoed-gavin-newsom&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24232172/california-ai-safety-bill-1047-vetoed-gavin-newsom" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24232172/california-ai-safety-bill-1047-vetoed-gavin-newsom</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-29T16:32:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-29T16:32:30-04:00</updated><title>漫威和 DC 失去“超级英雄”商标</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;书架上漫画书的图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/1AZTsMB3plwJ7I38SD6LV8I8wXw=/4x0:4924x3280/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73620113/2089852195.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption >;照片：John Carl D&#39;Annibale / Albany Times Union via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;F0Vvzd&quot;>;你知道漫威和 DC 几十年来如何共同拥有“超级英雄”的商标所有权？那个时代显然已经结束了，因为美国专利商标局已经取消了这些公司对其几个商标的主张，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reuters.com/legal/litigation/us-trademark-office -cancels-marvel-dcs-super-hero-marks-2024-09-26/&quot;>;路透社报道&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;uqo3kj&quot;>;取消来了这是 Superbabies Limited 挑战的结果，这是一家小公司，制作了一系列关于超级英雄婴儿的&lt;em>;Superbabies&lt;/em>;漫画。在 DC“试图阻止里奇尔德推广超级宝贝的努力”之后，《超级宝贝》的创作者 SJ 里奇德决定挑战这两个漫画巨头对商标的主张，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/ reichman-jorgensen-lehman--feldberg-triumphs-over-comic-giants-super-hero-trademarks-open-to-public-use-302260374.html&quot;>;在一份新闻稿中写下了代表 Richold 的律师事务所&lt;/a>; .&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;EqHKH7&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39; {“stories”：[{“title”：“迪士尼提起诉讼以保留其复仇者联盟版权”，“url”：“https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/24/22691842/disney-marvel-sues -comic-artist-iron-man-avengers&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&#39;Spinning&#39; 已注册商标，Peloton 对此并不满意&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2021/2/18/22289005/peloton-spinning-spin-trademark-mad-dogg-dispute-appeal&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;端庄而谨慎的商标调查&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www .theverge.com/24230813/demure-mindful-trademark-uspto-explainer-jools-lebron&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;fNMkkD&quot;>;漫威和 DC 没有在 2024 年 7 月 24 日截止日期之前未回应挑战，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24257677/marvel- dc-super-hero-trademark-canceled-challenge-superbabies&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24257677/marvel-dc-super-hero-trademark-canceled-challenge-superbabies" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/29/24257677/marvel-dc-super-hero-trademark-canceled-challenge-superbabies</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-29T13:08:02-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-29T13:08:02-04:00</updated><title>雷蛇通过新的游戏垫和振动耳机转向触觉</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;绿色和黑色背景上的 Razer Freyja 的图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/UebC2ja9eOozQDU2PSuIli-A0Y4=/0x0:1500x1000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73619620/Razer_Freyja.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Razer Freyja 可以将大多数电脑椅变成触觉游戏配件。&lt;/em>; |图片：Razer&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7R1EgY&quot;>;Razer 发布了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://razer.a9yw.net/c/482924/642901/10229?u=https% 3A%2F%2Fwww.razer.com%2Fgaming-chairs-accessories%2Frazer-freyja&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Freyja 游戏垫&lt;/a>;，触觉垫该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://press.razer.com/featured/razercon-2024/&quot;>;宣布&lt;/a>;。该坐垫售价 299.99 美元，现已上市。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;DEbH6V&quot;>;Freyja 是游戏控制器振动的延伸 - 除了摇动您的双手之外，它还让多个面板发出嗡嗡声位于您的身后和下方，以响应游戏中发生的事情。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;RJfAsz&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;instagram-media&quot; data-instgrm-captioned=&quot;&quot; data-instgrm- permalink=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/reel/C13OXfRsuX_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading&quot; data-instgrm-version=&quot;14&quot; style=&quot; 背景：#FFF；边框：0；边框半径:3px; 框阴影:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); 最大宽度:658px; :326px; 宽度:99.375%; 宽度:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px);&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;padding:16px;&quot;>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/reel/C13OXfRsuX_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading&quot; style=&quot;background:#FFFFFF; line-height:0; padding:0 0; text